      "cost_formula": "EML-∞ (exact); 1n (softplus/LEAd approximation)",
      "cost_at_N10": null,
      "note": "Use softplus ln(1+exp(x)) = LEAd(x,1) = 1n as smooth surrogate"
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
